org.kramerlab.vines

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kramerlab.vines.Node
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Node>

    public class Node
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Node>
    This is the Node class.
    In the Node class, we store the labeling of the Nodes and the (pseudo) observations.
    We also store the Nodes, where this Node is merged from, which enables to check the proximity condition.
    Author:
    Christian Lamberty (clamber@students.uni-mainz.de)
